# F√≥rmulas S√≠smicas ‚Äî N√∫cleo

## Velocidades
\(V_P = \sqrt{(K + \frac{4}{3}\mu)/\rho}\), \(V_S = \sqrt{\mu/\rho}\)

## Dist√¢ncia por Œît
\(\Delta \approx V_P V_S (t_S - t_P)/(V_P - V_S)\)

## Momento & Magnitude
\(M_0 = \mu A D\), \(\quad M_w=\frac{2}{3}\log_{10}(M_0) - 6{,}07\)

## Gutenberg‚ÄìRichter
\(\log_{10} N(M) = a - bM\)

## Atenua√ß√£o (geom√©trica + anelasticidade)
\(A(r,f) \propto r^{-1} \exp(-\pi f r/(Q V))\)

## GMPE (forma gen√©rica)
\(\ln(\text{PGA}) = c_0 + c_1M + c_2\ln(R + c_3 e^{c_4M}) + \ldots\)


